=== Notes ===

{{note|c1|1}} Compression is not a built-in feature of the formats, however, the resulting archive can be compressed with any algorithm of choice. Several implementations include functionality to do this automatically<br/>
{{note|c2|2}} Most implementations can optionally produce a self-extracting executable<br/>
{{note|c3|3}} Per-file compression with [[gzip]], [[bzip2]], [[lzo]], [[xz]], [[lzma]] (as opposed to compressing the whole archive). An individual can choose not to compress already compressed filenames based on their suffix as well.

